And can we start by talking about your family background?  
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid7756011 Glen:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid9184388\charrsid7756011 \tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid9184388\charrsid7756011 My father \'85
 grew up in Johnston County, in Ohio, that\rquote s not very far from Lake Erie, in farming country, and his father was a farmer.  That family line runs all the way back to Scotland, so that\rquote s one connection to Great Britain.  And then my mother
\rquote s side, my mother was born in Buffalo, she was the daughter of a [Northern Baptist] minister, a long line of [preachers], actually, going back to 1825.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid7756011 Paul:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid9184388\charrsid7756011 \tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid9184388\charrsid7756011 
And which Church is that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid7756011 Glen:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid4470500\charrsid7756011 \tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid9184388\charrsid7756011 
This would be the American Baptist, or the Northern Baptist, and her father was a Minister in Washington, DC, for 30 years, in the National Memorial Church there in Washington.  I remember visiting my grandparents, this must have been \'85 I was born in
\rquote 34, this must have been \rquote 41, and standing in the nave of the of the church, and watching my grandfather baptise someone in the front of the church \endash 
 one of those impressive churches with a large steeple.  I think it could hold something like 1500-2000 people.  
\par 
\par [TELEPHONE INTERRUPTION]
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid7756011 Glen:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid4470500\charrsid7756011 \tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid9184388\charrsid7756011 
