\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid7756011 Glen:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid4470500\charrsid7756011 \tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid9184388\charrsid7756011 I think he played t
he role of a Vice-President, but well, I don\rquote t know, first-hand, what he did.  He was always travelling, but I\rquote 
m not sure about the details though, in terms of what that Organisation did, with regard to film industry, connections between different countries and so on.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid7756011 Paul:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid9184388\charrsid7756011 \tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid9184388\charrsid7756011 
