Well, I can remember some of that, but they might have had me partially drugged so that I wouldn\rquote 
t experience that.  But I can visualise the room that I was in.  And then I remember doing all of this campaigning for the March of the Dimes and talking to people about the fact that I had come through it.  And it\rquote 
s a good organisation.  So I really felt identified.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid7756011 Paul:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid9184388\charrsid7756011 \tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid9184388\charrsid7756011 
