\b\f39\fs22\insrsid4470500\charrsid7756011 \tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid9184388\charrsid7756011 Well, I think that we have some good examples of it, actually.  One of my [former] students, Avshalom Caspi, used a wonderful
